            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <p class="pull-left">Copyright © 2017 NUKUTAKA Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
                    <p class="pull-right">Designed by <span><a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/tienphuc.nguyen.50">Quyễn Tiến Fúk</a></span></p>
                </div>
